en_169985_0	Opposition Leader and Leader of the Tamil National Alliance, R. Sampanthan said that they expect Indian to expedite the process of introducing a new constitution to Sri Lanka.
en_169985_1	Following a meeting with visiting Indian Foreign Minister Sushma Swaraj, Sampanthan said that the government was postponing the drafting of a new constitution citing various reasons.
en_169985_2	The Indian Foreign Minister was in the country to participate in the Indian Ocean Conference.
